===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|lang=fr|épilogue}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|lang=la|epilogus}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἐπίλογος||a conclusion, peroration of a speech, epilogue of a play|tr=epilogos|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ἐπιλέγειν||say in addition|tr=epilegein|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ἐπί||in addition|tr=epi|lang=grc}} + {{term|λέγειν||to say|tr=legein|lang=grc}}.

